        <h2>MacWispr 1.2.2</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Listening HUD</strong> — non-activating status pill (listening / transcribing / done)</li>
          <li><strong>Clear pipeline states</strong> — menu bar Ready → Listening → Transcribing → Done/Fail</li>
          <li><strong>Sound feedback</strong> — Tink start · Pop release · Glass success · Funk failure</li>
          <li><strong>Failure banner</strong> — Fix Accessibility / Open Setup when insert fails</li>
          <li><strong>Onboarding checklist</strong> — mic, Accessibility, hotkey, model</li>
          <li>Mode-specific controls · Copy / re-paste last result · Shortcuts / App Intents</li>
          <li>Developer ID signed</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
